WEBVTT

00:04:59.565 --> 00:05:01.140
Now you will ask,

00:05:01.164 --> 00:05:03.822
"Would people really
go through all this trouble?"

00:05:04.359 --> 00:05:07.718
I think they would if they had incentives,

00:05:07.742 --> 00:05:10.674
like loyalty points or cash back.

00:05:10.698 --> 00:05:12.908
Let's call it "green cash."

00:05:13.419 --> 00:05:16.572
There would be a whole
new opportunity to make money

00:05:16.596 --> 00:05:20.539
from this new customer base
looking to buy these returns.

00:05:21.026 --> 00:05:24.341
This system would make
a fun thing like shopping

00:05:24.365 --> 00:05:26.141
a spiritual experience

00:05:26.165 --> 00:05:28.810
that helps save our planet.

00:05:28.834 --> 00:05:31.434
(Applause)